r&gt;If you don’t know whether you have fog, go from PoK to West Freeport during Norrathian DAYTIME and see which of the two screenshots better represents what you see there. The bottom line is this: if in the Freeport newbie yard you don't see wall to wall, you have fog.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;/em waits for the fog fix since March 2004.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Gwyth</description>
